        <p>First described and edited by <bibl>
            <ptr target="bib:Ramachandranb"></ptr>
          </bibl>, then re-edited by the same author in <bibl><ptr target="bib:Ramachandran1953"></ptr>: <citedRange>28</citedRange></bibl>; our edition is based on the latter. Re-edited here from our photos of the ASI estampage.</p>
